e a retrospective that covers:\n1. **Session summary** — no-op session, state corruption fix #24\n2. **Issues analysis** — the recurring state corruption is the ONLY issue. Ralph must be killed.\n3. **Cost analysis** — from the cost report, note that the last 24 sessions have been wasted spend fixing the same corruption\n4. **What went well** — fast diagnosis, efficient fix\n5. **What went wrong** — ralph still running with stale state, 24th occurrence\n6. **Lessons learned** — ralph needs a mechanism to detect sprint completion and self-terminate\n7. **Action items** — KILL RALPH. The sprint is done.\n\nWrite the retrospective to _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md. Since a retro for today already exists, append to it with a `---` separator and timestamp.\n\nDo NOT ask the user any questions — proceed autonomously.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","agentId":"a2163fb7db98a575e","agentType":"general-purpose","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrospective for session 40 appended to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md`.\n\nSummary: Same no-op as the previous 9 sessions. State corruption fix #24 for stories 16-5 through 16-8. Total sprint cost is now $693.45, with an estimated $210 (30%) wasted on 24 identical fix cycles. All 74 stories and 17 epics remain done. The only action item that matters: kill Ralph."}],"totalDurationMs":74498,"totalTokens":28799,"totalToolUseCount":9,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2013,"cache_read_input_tokens":26645,"output_tokens":140,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2013},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
